cc5efa47-fd90-4099-93f9-5340a93c9b9d.1abe18a6-7144-49b8-bf15-99aec3881784.description=
This workflow adds the resource bindings for the resource offerings attached to the infrastructure component to its child components, appropriately. It creates resource binding for a uCMDB based resource offering to the sever group components and  resource binding for uCMDB, SiteScope and SA Compute based resource offerings to the server components, if the offering exists on the infrastructure service component.

Inputs\:
srvGrpList		- CSA Component Id of one or more server group (delimited by pipe | operator) on which the uCMDB resource binding is to be created 
		  Eg \: ||....
srvList		- CSA Component Id of one or more server (delimited by pipe | operator) on which the uCMDB, SiteScope, SA resource bindings are to be created
		  Eg \: ||....
userIdentifier	- CSA User Identifier 
infraComponentId	- CSA Component Id of the infrastructure service component. The resource bindings available on this component are attached to its child sever group and server 			  components.

Responses\:
success - Workflow completed successfully.
failure - Something went wrong.
cc5efa47-fd90-4099-93f9-5340a93c9b9d.41de4ff5-0750-4928-bbea-0efad739a347.prompt=User Identifier cc5efa47-fd90-4099-93f9-5340a93c9b9d.45420e6f-5b62-4ea8-a221-36dd34541eaa.description=
This workflow adds the MOE servers as child components to the existing server group component on CSA

Inputs\:

serverGroupName	- Name of the MOE server group to which the server components are to be added
svcInstanceId	- CSA Service Instance Id
ioXml		- Output XML returned by the MOE Add Server or Create Service API calls
serverGroupId	- CSA Component Id of the server group to which the MOE servers are to be added
userIdentifier	- CSA User Identifier

Responses\:
success - Workflow completed successfully.
failure - Something went wrong.
cc5efa47-fd90-4099-93f9-5340a93c9b9d.5abbd487-9806-4c6c-a0ad-0efd4d1933ef.description=
Checks to see if a list contains every element in another list.

Inputs\:
sublist -The contained list.
container - The containing list.
delimiter - A delimiter separating elements in the two lists. Default is a comma
ignoreCase - If set to 'True' then the compare is not case sensitive. Default is True

Responses\:
true - sublist is contained in container.
false - sublist is not contained in container.

Results\:
Result - All items contained in the sublist that are not in the container.
cc5efa47-fd90-4099-93f9-5340a93c9b9d.9ffd042b-1367-44c6-8faf-303d957ee92c.description=
This workflow adds public actions on the server groups and server components. It adds Add Server and Add Disk actions at the server group level and Power on/off server at the server component level.

Inputs\:
srvGrpList		- CSA Component Id of one or more server group to which the public actions ( Add Server and Add Disk ) are to be attached delimited by pipe | operator
		  Eg \: ||....
srvList		- CSA Component Id of one or more server to which the public actions ( Power on Server and Power off Server ) are to be attached delimited by pipe | operator
		  Eg \: ||....
userIdentifier	- CSA User Identifier 
RSC_PROVIDER_ID	- CSA Resource Provider Id for the MOE provider

Responses\:
success - Workflow completed successfully.
failure - Something went wrong.

cc5efa47-fd90-4099-93f9-5340a93c9b9d.description=

Add CSA Server Components to the Server Group Components. The Server Group Components are childs of Software Application Tier Components.

Input Parameters\:

tierId - Software Application Tier Component Id.
serverGrpList - List of Server Group Component Ids . Each Component Id is separated by "," delimiter.
ioXML - Output XML returned by the MOE Add Server or Create Service API calls
userIdentifier - User Identifier token Id from CSA.
svcInstanceId - Service Instance token Id 
appComponentId - Software Application Tier Component Id.
providerId - Resource Provider Id that needs to stored on the Server Component.

Responses\:
success - Workflow completed successfully.
failure - Something went wrong.
flow.name: Add Servers to Tier
